Package: ExaGeoStatCPP
Type: Package
Title: R Package demonstrates the R/C++ Language Interface for Exascale GeoStatistics software (ExaGeoStat)
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2024-01-14
Author: Mahmoud ElKarargy [aut, cph], Sameh Abdulah [cre, cph], KAUST King Abdullah University of Science and Technology [fnd, cph], Brightskies [cph]
Maintainer: Sameh Abdulah <sameh.abdulah@kaust.edu.sa>
Description: An R-Interface for the ExaGeoStatCPP software: a parallel high performance unified framework for geostatistics on  manycore systems. Its abbreviation stands for Exascale Geostatistics. The framework aims at optimizing the likelihood function for a given spatial data to provide an efficient way to predict missing observations. The framework targets many-core systems: clusters of CPUs and GPUs.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports: assertthat (>= 0.2.1), MASS, methods, Rcpp (>= 1.0.9)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), assertthat (>= 0.2.1)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
SystemRequirements: C++ (>= 11), CMake (>= 3.2), lapacke (https://github.com/xianyi/OpenBLAS/releases)
NeedsCompilation: yes
OS_type: unix
